'''2015年[[全英音乐奖|全英音乐奖]]'''於2015年2月25日举办，本届为第35届[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]年度流行音乐奖项，典礼于[[伦敦|伦敦]][[O2体育馆|O2体育馆]]举行，[[安东尼·马克派特宁|安东尼·马克派特宁]]和[[德克兰·当纳利|德克兰·当纳利]]（Ant & Dec）联合主持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-29820472|title=Ant and Dec to host 2015 Brit awards|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-12-30|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228033800/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-29820472|dead-url=no}}</ref>。提名作品于2015年1月15日公布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/brit-awards-2015-the-nominations-in-full-9980900.html|title=Brit Awards 2015: The nominations in full|publisher=The Independent|date=2015-01-15|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227204323/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/brit-awards-2015-the-nominations-in-full-9980900.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[翠西·艾敏|翠西·艾敏]]成为第五位设计奖杯雕塑的艺术家<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brits.co.uk/news/tracey-emin-to-style-brits-statue|title=Tracy Emin to style BRITs Statue|publisher=BRIT Awards 2015|date=2014-12-03|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2014-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227194507/http://www.brits.co.uk/news/tracey-emin-to-style-brits-statue|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

