== 典礼花絮 ==
=== 威斯特表演被和谐 ===
典礼举办前一天快要结束时，[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]被确认将登台表演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a631336/kanye-west-to-perform-at-tonights-brit-awards.html#~p5m5b93RPQ36Ak |title=Kanye West to perform at tonight's Brit Awards |work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225222307/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a631336/kanye-west-to-perform-at-tonights-brit-awards.html#~p5m5b93RPQ36Ak |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他表演其歌曲《All Day》时配备了大批穿着黑衣服举着火焰喷射器的随从。然而，他的表演中整首歌被多次静音，都是些歌曲中非常露骨的歌词，[[独立电视台|独立电视台]]的直播屏蔽了饶舌中反复用的“黑鬼”（nigger），照顾电视观众<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2015/feb/25/brit-awards-2015-red-carpet-ceremony-winners-live|title=Brit awards 2015: the red carpet, ceremony and winners – as it happened|date=2015-02-25|work=Guardian|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226142933/http://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2015/feb/25/brit-awards-2015-red-carpet-ceremony-winners-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

对此，观众的反映有所不同，主持人Ant & Dec之后拿它开玩笑，而社交媒体上的意见出现分歧，有些人批评威斯特的表演，有些人批评ITV处理问题的做法<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2969478/Kanye-West-leaves-Taylor-Swift-Lionel-Richie-open-mouthed-use-N-word-BRITs-performance-broadcast-live-viewers-complain-ITV-muting-show.html |title=Kanye West leaves Taylor Swift and Lionel Richie open-mouthed as his use of the N-word during BRITs performance is broadcast live... as viewers complain about ITV muting the show |work=Mail Online |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226040649/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2969478/Kanye-West-leaves-Taylor-Swift-Lionel-Richie-open-mouthed-use-N-word-BRITs-performance-broadcast-live-viewers-complain-ITV-muting-show.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/live/entertainment-arts-31430677|title=Brit Awards 2015: as it happened|date=2015-02-25|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226193407/http://www.bbc.com/news/live/entertainment-arts-31430677|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 麦当娜摔跤 ===
[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]在当晚的压轴表演中演唱其单曲《[[Living_for_Love|Living for Love]]》以结束晚会，这标志着她20年来首次献唱全英音乐奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/feb/03/madonna-perform-at-brit-awards-2015 |title=Madonna to perform at 2015 Brit awards |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2015-02-03 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203215028/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/feb/03/madonna-perform-at-brit-awards-2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，在表演刚开始时，她的服装出现了问题，被舞台的一部分台阶给绊倒<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2969176/The-moment-Madonna-56-falls-BACKWARDS-set-steps-pulled-dancers-BRIT-Awards.html|title=Should've undone the Material, Girl! Madonna, 56, is pulled backwards off the stage down a set of steps by her cape during shocking BRIT Awards 2015 finale performance|date=2015-02-25|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226110148/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2969176/The-moment-Madonna-56-falls-BACKWARDS-set-steps-pulled-dancers-BRIT-Awards.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事后她发布[[Instagram|Instagram]]证实自己相安无事，并附文“感谢大家的祝愿！我没事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-31633349 |title=Brit Awards 2015: Madonna falls off stage |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225202005/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-31633349 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”后来据透露，她的斗篷绑得太紧了，舞者试图帮她从脖子上解开时，不料让她摔在地上，吓到了观众<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/brit-awards/11436018/Madonna-falls-off-stage-at-the-Brit-Awards.html|title=Madonna falls off stage at the Brit Awards|date=2015-02-25|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226053559/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/brit-awards/11436018/Madonna-falls-off-stage-at-the-Brit-Awards.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。几秒钟后，她按计划继续表演<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/music/madonna-takes-a-major-onstage-tumble-at-the-brit-112079529441.html |title=Madonna Takes a Major Onstage Tumble at the BRIT Awards |work=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226051045/https://www.yahoo.com/music/madonna-takes-a-major-onstage-tumble-at-the-brit-112079529441.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

